567,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Dominique Maher is an actress, known for Doctor Who (2005), The Red Sea Diving Resort (2019) and American Monster (2016).","name":"Dominique Maher","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Доминик Маэр","primary":false}}]}},"person_2318996_translations":{"at":1773689202036,"data":{"id":2318996,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Celinde Schoenmaker","primary":true}}]}},"person_1737040_translations":{"at":1773689203483,"data":{"id":1737040,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Maxwell Acee Donovan (born May 14, 2005) is an American actor.","name":"Maxwell Acee Donovan","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}},"person_1118078_translations":{"at":1773689203769,"data":{"id":1118078,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Ellyn Jameson","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Элли Джеймисон","primary":false}}]}},"person_1368507_translations":{"at":1773689204411,"data":{"id":1368507,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth Dean Lail (born on March 25, 1992, in Williamson County, Texas) is an American actress. Known for her role as Anna in the ABC adventure fantasy TV series 'Once Upon a Time', Guinevere Beck on Netflix's thriller 'You', & Vanessa in Five Nights at Freddy's films.","name":"Elizabeth Lail","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth Dean Lail nasceu em Williamson County, Texas. Seus pais são Dean Lail e Kay Surratt. Ela tem uma irmã, Kathryn. Mudou-se com sua família para Asheboro, Carolina do Norte ainda na infância.\n\nApós terminar o ensino médio na Asheboro High School, Elizabeth começou a estudar interpretação em 2010 na University of North Carolina School of the Arts, se formando em maio de 2014.\n\nAtualmente mora em Nova Iorque.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Елізабет Леіл","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Elizabeth Dean Lail, née le 25 mars 1992, est une actrice américaine. Elle est principalement connue pour son interprétation d'Anna dans la série télévisée Once Upon a Time diffusée sur la chaîne ABC, ainsi que pour son rôle dans la série You.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"伊丽莎白·迪恩·莱尔（Elizabeth Dean Lail）（生于1992年3月25日）是美国女演员。她以在ABC冒险幻想电视连续剧《从前》中扮演安娜的角色而闻名。\n\n莱尔（Lail）生于得克萨斯州威廉姆森县（Williamson County），由她的父母，迪安·富兰克林·莱尔（Dean Franklin Lail）和妻子凯（Kay Lurene Surratt）所生。她有一个姐姐。 Lail在北卡罗来纳州的阿什伯勒长大。她于2009年从阿什伯勒高中毕业后，于2014年5月毕业于北卡罗来纳大学艺术学院。\n\n莱尔大学毕业后立即主要从事学生电影作品的制作，例如《飞机模型》和《没有》。[需要引用]她在美国广播公司的电影《曾几何时》中试镜后，搬到纽约从事舞台演出。她在该系列的第四季中饰演安娜。莱尔（Lail）在《自由形式》恐怖系列的“夏日之死”（Dead of Summer）中扮演主角，扮演集中营顾问艾米（Amy）的角色。 2017年7月27日，莱恩（Lail）在终身电视连续剧《你》（You）中担任女主角，与宾·巴格利（Penn Badgley）对面。","name":"伊丽莎白·莱尔","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"엘리자베스 레일","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"伊麗莎白·迪恩·萊爾（Elizabeth Dean Lail）（生於 1992 年 3 月 25 日）是美國女演員。她以在 ABC 冒險幻想電視聯續劇《從前》中扮演安娜的角色而聞名。\n\n萊爾（Lail）生於得克薩斯州威廉姆森縣（Williamson County），由她的父母，迪安·富蘭克林·萊爾（Dean Franklin Lail）和妻子凱（Kay Lurene Surratt）所生。她有一個姐姐。\n\nLail 在北卡羅來納州的阿什伯勒長大。她於 2009 年從阿什伯勒高中畢業後，於 2014 年 5 月畢業於北卡羅來納大學藝術學院。\n\n萊爾大學畢業後立即主要從事學生電影作品的製作，例如《飛機模型》和《沒有》。[需要引用]她在美國廣播公司的電影《廣莫雲遊錄》中試鏡後，搬到紐約從事舞台演出。她在該系列的第四季中飾演安娜。萊爾（Lail）在《自由形式》恐怖系列的“夏日之死”（Dead of Summer）中扮演主角，扮演集中營顧問艾米（Amy）的角色。\n\n2017 年 7 月 27 日，萊恩（Lail）在終身電視聯續劇《你》（You）中擔任女主角，與賓·巴格利（Penn Badgley）對面。","name":"伊麗莎白·萊爾","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"💥Элизабет Дин Лэил. Родилась в 1992-ом году в Уэйко, Техас, США. Росла в семье со старшей сестрой. Отец работал юристом, а мать была домохозяйкой. Училась в Школе искусств Университета Северной Каролины. Работает актрисой. С 2021-го замужем за нейрохирургом Ниеку Маншади, детей у пары нет\n\n🎬Главные проекты🎬: «Пять ночей с Фредди» (2023), «Ты» (2018), «Обратный отсчёт» (2019)\n\n⭐Интересный факт⭐: Элизабет выросла в христианской семье и с детства мечтала о театре","name":"Элизабет Лэил","primary":false}}]}},"tv_16347_keywords":{"at":1773689207058,"data":{"id":16347,"results":[{"name":"monster","id":1299},{"name":"samurai","id":1462},{"name":"family clan","id":7629},{"name":"superhero","id":9715},{"name":"mecha","id":10046},{"name":"giant robot","id":10891},{"name":"giant monster","id":11100},{"name":"demon","id":15001},{"name":"super power","id":33637},{"name":"superhero team","id":155030},{"name":"ronin","id":155198},{"name":"kaiju","id":161791},{"name":"youkai","id":196509},{"name":"feudal lord","id":197283},{"name":"super sentai","id":283547},{"name":"henshin hero